# Walkthrough: Dobot Nova 5 Driver Update for New Firmware

## Summary
Updated the ROS driver to work with the new Dobot controller firmware where **port 30003 (motion) is closed** and all commands go through **port 29999**.

## Changes Made

### 1. [dobot_api.py](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py)
- `DobotApi.__init__` now accepts `existing_socket` param for socket sharing
- [DobotApiDashboard](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#54-494) gained all motion methods ([MovJ](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#383-398), [MovL](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#399-414), [JointMovJ](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#533-548), [MoveJog](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#650-666), [Sync](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup.py#415-420), etc.)
- [DobotApiMove](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#495-735) updated to use new firmware syntax
- **Command syntax changes:**

| Old Syntax | New Syntax |
|-----------|-----------|
| [MovJ(x,y,z,rx,ry,rz)](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#383-398) | [MovJ(pose={x,y,z,rx,ry,rz})](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#383-398) |
| [MovL(x,y,z,rx,ry,rz)](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#399-414) | [MovL(pose={x,y,z,rx,ry,rz})](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#399-414) |
| [JointMovJ(j1,...,j6)](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#533-548) | [MovJ(joint={j1,...,j6})](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#383-398) |

